high_descs: move to the table in the opposite corner of the room
pick up bread from the table
move to the fridge to the left from the sink
chill the bread in the fridge for a moment
move to the counter across from the sink
put the bread on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put chilled bread on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go as far as the door then turn left and go almost to the wall then turn right and go to the table and turn left
Pick up the loaf of bread in the middle of the table
Turn left and go towards the garbage can then turn left and go towards the door then turn right and go to the fridge
Put the bread on the top shelf in the fridge and wait a bit, then take the bread out of the fridge
Turn right, then turn right again and go to the counter
Put the bread on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled bread on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn around and then to the left and go straight back. Turn to the right and face the white table on the left.
Pick up the bread from the center of the table.
Carry the bread and turn to the left. Find the fridge on the right.
Open the fridge and place the bread inside. Shut the door then open the door and take the bread out. Shut the door again.
Take the bread and turn around to the counter.
Place the bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Chill bread and place it on the counter.
